As my experince showed M.T.T (Main Tank Tactics) and C.H.R (Complete Heal Rotations) are the best tactics to bring high level encounter down. <br>
<br>
M.T.T.<br>
<br>
The idea of M.T.T is that only one Tank need to be complete healed. <br>
How you archieve this? Its quite easy the Main Tank (declared by Raid Leader (AC, Weapons, Level)) should taunt as only person and build agro before all other engage the mob. All other Melees attack the mob at the max. attack range. Why? Cause as farest you away from the mob less agro you produce.<br>
<br>
This idea i got of a melee board. They suggested to make a hotbutton like this one:<br>
<br>
hotkey name( up to you any you like ) <br>
Line 1: /discipline defensive <br>
Line 2: /pause 600* <br>
Line 3: /pause 520* <br>
Line 4: /tell xxxxxx (Main Tank 2) my def gone in 5 sec,move up taunt and open defensive plz!! <br>
Line 5: /gu my def gone ,change your target to xxxxxx (Main Tank 2) for CH plz!! <br>
<br>
*10 = 1 sec<br>
<br>
